      <h2 class="section" id="mission">Mission <a href="#mission" class="anchor">#</a></h2>
      <p class="section-meta">Verbatim lab statement. Quote directly when needed.</p>
      <p>Design innovative and responsible AI-driven solutions that improve developer
      productivity while addressing the twin challenges of transparency and resource
      efficiency. Practical advances, rigorous methods, open collaboration.</p>

      <h2 class="section" id="research">Research avenues <a href="#research" class="anchor">#</a></h2>
      <p class="section-meta">Four primary directions and one supporting direction.</p>
      <ol class="avenues">
        <li id="avenue-explainability"><div class="num">01</div><div class="body"><span class="name">Explainability &amp; Interpretability</span><p>Methods that reveal how code models reason &mdash; rationales, traces, tests &mdash; so developers can inspect, trust, and debug automation.</p></div></li>
        <li id="avenue-efficiency"><div class="num">02</div><div class="body"><span class="name">Efficiency &amp; Resource-Aware Automation</span><p>Quantization, distillation, and PEFT to deliver low-latency, memory-light, cost-aware automation measured on real workloads with reproducible metrics.</p></div></li>
        <li id="avenue-agents"><div class="num">03</div><div class="body"><span class="name">Multi-Agent LLMs for SE</span><p>Role-aligned agents that plan, code, test, and review &mdash; coordinated to produce coherent, end-to-end developer assistance.</p></div></li>
        <li id="avenue-neurosymbolic"><div class="num">04</div><div class="body"><span class="name">Neurosymbolic AI for SE</span><p>Hybrid pipelines pairing LLMs with program analysis and constraints to produce interpretable, checkable fixes, tests, and designs.</p></div></li>
        <li class="secondary" id="avenue-task-aware"><div class="num">05</div><div class="body"><span class="name">Task-Aware Code Automation <span class="chip" style="margin-left:6px">supporting</span></span><p>From issues, diffs, and traces to concise summaries, TODOs, and plans; models that reduce developer toil with actionable, repo-aware guidance.</p></div></li>
      </ol>

